            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p><p>Once done, transfer the <strong>toasted seeds</strong> to a plate and reserve the pan</p>",
